@page "/about"

<PageTitle>Trip Planner — About</PageTitle>

<BrandSurface Eyebrow="About Trip Planner" Title="A private home for your travel plans" Class="mb-4">
    <p class="lead mb-0">Trip Planner helps individual travelers turn scattered ideas into a clear, private itinerary without sharing personal trip data on public surfaces.</p>
</BrandSurface>

<div class="row g-3 mt-2">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100 modern-card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="brand-eyebrow">Personal by default</p>
                <h2 class="h5">Your trips stay in your account</h2>
                <p class="mb-0 text-secondary">Trips, legs, and tracked items stay tied to your account, and no personal data is shown on public pages.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100 modern-card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="brand-eyebrow">Everything in one place</p>
                <h2 class="h5">Plan by car, train, plane, or boat</h2>
                <p class="mb-0 text-secondary">Consolidate all of your trip information — hotels, excursions, transportation, and dining — into one place. Keep every stay, activity, reservation, and travel leg together on one timeline so every day of your trip is easy to follow.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100 modern-card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="brand-eyebrow">Better together</p>
                <h2 class="h5">Share trips with your travel companions</h2>
                <p class="mb-0 text-secondary">Traveling with a partner or a group? Share a trip so others can follow along as a Viewer or help build the plan as a Collaborator. You stay in control — invite registered people, change their access, or remove it at any time.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
